	<h5 class="success"><u> 04/24/18 Changelog:</u></h5>
	<ul>
		<li>Added the ability to narrow down choices by manufacturer</li>
		<li>Added fFreeform steel coaster. It randomly selects from EVERYTHING. It will contradict itself.</li>
	</ul>
</div>
